{"tid":1718470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]防止被自殺- telegram版實時追蹤系統","createTime":"2019-11-14T00:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:34.000Z","uid":55627,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5280f943a1c94842a17a354e336e5c9540adcb1c","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"昨日收到新聞講6月到9月有2537 宗個案<br />\n加埋自殺個案平均一個月死接近1000人<br />\n雖然現階段搵唔到証據確實証明佢地既死亡原因<br />\n但係大家見佢地既死狀都會十分懷疑是否 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他殺</span><br />\n<br />\n大家不論發夢, 出街, 什至放工番屋企都會驚會唔會比人無啦啦捉左去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強姦, 輪姦, 自殺, 或者被自殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係度想分享一個近來確保家人回家安全既方法<br />\n就算和理非都可以確保每個人安全回家<br />\n<br />\n所需軟件: telegram<br />\n1. 離開時候, 搵你相信既人既telegram對話, 㩒以下既制<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5USDtj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5USDtj.png&h=d30d7d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 選擇分享你既位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8zLd1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8zLd1N.png&h=29a9ed17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 分享實時位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCRxDtz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCRxDtz.png&h=9f3fd3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 一路開住番屋企, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沿途保持聯絡</span></span>, 有需要可以lock 機, 不過要確保whatsapp 運行<br />\n<br />\n5. 確認番到屋企後, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問對方特別問題</span></span>, 確認對方係其本人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n***我唔知道呢個方法會唔會有反效果, 但係我實在好驚我屋企人被自殺同埋輪姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 希望分享用呢個方法確保大家安全番到屋企, 希望討論下可行性<br />\n<br />\n***之前分享過whatsapp 版, 不過巴打話會出賣資料, telegram 應該會好啲<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩<br />\n六大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"96d47d19f8b86d470ef32029800095b13a883440","tid":1718470,"uid":303499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d85634d665aca8191f2540b37beb560b96a0f248","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:10:51.000Z","msg":"0/5"},{"pid":"5b49bf70f076c28942d5d8044d5aeea179790054","tid":1718470,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8649707e362a0604cdcc802e46135355906770fe","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"1/5"},{"pid":"683cb4a6c2d01252ef16dddac765c2ab2fb3a99b","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"8ce3c057c47ca03987e536b2e9035710437e6851","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"a45322bba518367c4b66225f8f7b75466e8f086e","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"4/5"},{"pid":"07c8bc98454f331df3aaffd5a434d4921b5d5d92","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"5/5"},{"pid":"2384b72a188f6ae5063cb734f3fed48924b50062","tid":1718470,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"好過whatsapp嘅share live location?"},{"pid":"a2b30e4ee18fff801ecc73c54b3d37af6e5cc2e6","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2384b72a188f6ae5063cb734f3fed48924b50062","tid":1718470,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"好過whatsapp嘅share live location?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"我諗唔驚泄流個人資料既<br />\n準繩度高"},{"pid":"cbb2c6f36ca819c235aac430a283b1d17051f84e","tid":1718470,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2384b72a188f6ae5063cb734f3